  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air, then boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>sweet potato[es] </strong>(skins on) into bite-sized pieces, the add them to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> over a high heat and bring to the boil and cook for 10-12 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once done, drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1721994271295-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-2-1721994271295-x400.jpg",
