            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>flattened chicken</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 9-10 min on each side or until charred and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3? Use two pans!</p>",
