      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
